1
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:13,920
Give me the blade.

2
00:00:24,560 --> 00:00:25,480
What are you doing?

3
00:00:25,720 --> 00:00:26,520
Watch this.

4
00:00:35,800 --> 00:00:37,400
This is called Heart-Devouring Gu.

5
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:40,000
It must be nourished with heart's blood.

6
00:00:40,360 --> 00:00:41,120
If the gu lives,

7
00:00:41,800 --> 00:00:42,480
you live.

8
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:47,400
Take good care of it.

9
00:00:48,480 --> 00:00:50,400
This gu only lives for three months.

10
00:00:51,120 --> 00:00:51,760
Make sure

11
00:00:52,040 --> 00:00:53,160
you don't let it die.

12
00:01:11,770 --> 00:01:14,200
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 5]

13
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:24,160
Nine.

14
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:25,720
Ten.

15
00:01:47,740 --> 00:01:53,460
♪In my dreams,
I walked to the edge of the sky♪

16
00:01:55,260 --> 00:02:00,260
♪Gazing at the Wangchen Spring♪

17
00:02:02,020 --> 00:02:07,260
♪My calling sank into the blue heavens♪

18
00:02:08,740 --> 00:02:12,540
♪By the shore,
my eyes were soaked with tears♪

19
00:02:13,820 --> 00:02:19,280
♪I watch you descend
to the mortal world♪

20
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,680
Are you in there?

21
00:02:21,060 --> 00:02:28,620
♪Slowly I let go of the thread I hold♪

22
00:02:29,420 --> 00:02:35,500
♪If immortals can't linger for love♪

23
00:02:35,820 --> 00:02:38,680
♪If mortals can't bind fate
for affection♪

24
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,480
Yaoyang.

25
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:40,720
You

26
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,080
are inside.

27
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:43,680
Right?

28
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:47,320
I know

29
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:48,720
you

30
00:02:48,900 --> 00:02:50,680
lock yourself in here

31
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,920
whenever you're upset.

32
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:57,360
Are you avoiding me?

33
00:02:58,900 --> 00:02:59,720
I just...

34
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:02,560
I don't know what came over me earlier.

35
00:03:04,900 --> 00:03:05,600
I promise

36
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:08,000
I'll never act like that again.

37
00:03:09,620 --> 00:03:10,800
Let's pinky swear.

38
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,480
Please come out, alright?

39
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,480
Don't be angry anymore.

40
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:40,880
The Heart-Devouring Gu

41
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,680
is also known as the Lover's Gu.

42
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:44,320
Once you develop feelings,

43
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,440
its poison

44
00:03:46,440 --> 00:03:48,760
will slowly seep into your heart.

45
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:51,120
You'll endure a heart-wrenching pain

46
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:53,080
until the poison takes your life.

47
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:56,120
Make sure you don't die

48
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,640
before your master even returns.

49
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:58,960
So

50
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:00,920
I can't develop feelings for her.

51
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,240
Then can she...?

52
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:03,920
Of course
she mustn't fall for you either.

53
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:06,800
She's only sustained by a wisp of

54
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,120
your master's remnant soul.

55
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:09,800
She is incomplete in spirit,

56
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:11,840
incapable of affection or love.

57
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,360
Your heart's blood

58
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:15,280
merely nourishes her flesh and blood.

59
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:17,720
You must first make her whole.

60
00:04:18,260 --> 00:04:20,360
Then implant the memories
from the remaining soul fragments.

61
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:23,560
Only then will she be truly revived.

62
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:25,200
Understood?

63
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,120
I'm...

64
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:29,920
I'm sorry.

65
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:44,280
Things never go according to plan.

66
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,240
Xiyin.

67
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:18,800
You bad guy!

68
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,240
She actually harbors

69
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:24,240
a trace of Xiyin's soul within her.

70
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,320
Martial Uncle,
why are you here drinking alone?

71
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:34,120
Is it because of
what happened last time?

72
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,120
I know.

73
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:40,000
If I speak of it, you will blame me.

74
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,160
But this matter is of great importance.

75
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,720
That day, Immortal Xiyin...

76
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:44,720
No.

77
00:05:44,820 --> 00:05:46,400
That woman who looks exactly like

78
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:47,360
Immortal Xiyin.

79
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,120
Xieyun was clearly...

80
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:49,640
Stop talking!

81
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,160
The Immortal Venerable cares most
about that evil creature.

82
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:56,560
She'll find out sooner or later.

83
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:57,480
Then we might as well...

84
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:58,320
I will

85
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:00,960
handle this myself.

86
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,920
Even if the Immortal Venerable
finds out,

87
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:05,120
I will bear all responsibility.

88
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,720
Say no more.

89
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:08,880
I have matters to attend to. I must go.

90
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,120
Martial Uncle, but...

91
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,400
You're up.

92
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:32,880
Let me show you

93
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:34,080
my swordplay.

94
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,960
Why has he been

95
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,360
so cold to me lately?

96
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:58,320
Go on.

97
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,280
Ruoxi.

98
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:05,160
How about

99
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:08,120
I take you to the mortal realm today?

100
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:08,720
The mortal realm?

101
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,160
Alright.

102
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:23,160
Ruoxi, look over there.

103
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:26,920
It's been so long since my last visit

104
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,400
to the mortal realm.

105
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,080
If you like it,

106
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,160
I can

107
00:07:31,400 --> 00:07:32,520
bring you here often in the future.

108
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:33,720
Really?

109
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,240
Great!

110
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:37,200
Tanghulu!

111
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,960
Tanghulu!

112
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,320
Yaoyang, money.

113
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,920
I didn't bring any money.

114
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,480
Yaoyang always pays.

115
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:54,120
Sir.

116
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:55,320
Alright.

117
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:56,120
Help yourself.

118
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:58,160
Alright. I'm off.

119
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,120
Tanghulu!

120
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:03,320
Is it good?

121
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:06,320
Just as delicious as last time.

122
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,160
You have a bite too.

123
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,440
Sugar figurine.

124
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,320
Miss, how about a sugar figurine?

125
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:24,600
In the mortal world,

126
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:27,680
you need money to buy anything.

127
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:29,720
Eat up.

128
00:08:33,660 --> 00:08:35,120
Sir, I'll have one.

129
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:35,560
Wait.

130
00:08:36,040 --> 00:08:37,000
Sugar figurines

131
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:39,120
are just pretty, not tasty.

132
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,080
Let's go over there.

133
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:55,400
I want to

134
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:56,800
ask you something.

135
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:58,960
What is it?

136
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,040
Yuxun said

137
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:03,120
that if you like someone,

138
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:05,280
you want to be with them
every single day.

139
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:07,000
If one day,

140
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,280
someone

141
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:10,160
doesn't want to be with the other,

142
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,480
does it mean
they don't love them anymore?

143
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,120
Why the sudden question?

144
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:16,400
Lately,

145
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:18,280
Yaoyang has suddenly become
really distant.

146
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:19,280
Do you think

147
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,720
he doesn't like me anymore?

148
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,320
Do you care about him a lot?

149
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:31,240
Of course.

150
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,960
I care about him the most.

151
00:09:39,040 --> 00:09:41,160
If they're slow to respond,

152
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,360
maybe there's a reason.

153
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:46,280
Maybe he...

154
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,120
Maybe he what?

155
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,600
Romantic feelings
between a man and a woman

156
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,480
are complicated.

157
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,920
It's not something that can be explained
in a few words.

158
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:02,680
Oh,

159
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:03,920
does the book

160
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,720
"Neither Red nor Green"

161
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:06,600
have the answer?

162
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:07,880
Teach me now.

163
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:09,280
Maybe then I'll understand.

164
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:10,680
Well...

165
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:11,760
How about

166
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:13,520
we go home right now and learn?

167
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:15,880
Ruoxi,

168
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,120
there's no rush.

169
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,120
Oh right,

170
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,400
there's a pastry shop over there.

171
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:20,800
Their pastries are especially delicious.

172
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:21,920
I'll go buy some for you.

173
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,000
Wait here for me.

174
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:40,160
Ruoxi.

175
00:11:07,780 --> 00:11:10,520
♪What is flickering?♪

176
00:11:10,740 --> 00:11:13,260
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

177
00:11:13,420 --> 00:11:19,260
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

178
00:11:19,300 --> 00:11:22,140
♪What is falling?♪

179
00:11:22,580 --> 00:11:25,380
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

180
00:11:25,620 --> 00:11:30,820
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

181
00:11:31,740 --> 00:11:33,340
♪When petals drift down♪

182
00:11:33,380 --> 00:11:34,840
♪When the rain falls all around♪

183
00:11:34,940 --> 00:11:37,540
♪I gaze into your eyes♪

184
00:11:37,700 --> 00:11:39,400
♪Beyond the dunes♪

185
00:11:39,500 --> 00:11:40,780
♪No end in sight♪

186
00:11:40,780 --> 00:11:43,780
♪I am like a mayfly♪

187
00:11:43,940 --> 00:11:45,340
♪I won't ask what the future holds♪

188
00:11:45,380 --> 00:11:46,840
♪Nor will I run away♪

189
00:11:46,860 --> 00:11:49,800
♪Through all seasons by my side♪

190
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:55,060
♪Searching for sparks in the dust♪

191
00:12:09,380 --> 00:12:12,120
♪What is flickering?♪

192
00:12:12,340 --> 00:12:14,820
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

193
00:12:15,020 --> 00:12:20,820
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

194
00:12:21,260 --> 00:12:24,060
♪What is falling?♪

195
00:12:24,180 --> 00:12:27,000
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

196
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:32,220
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

197
00:12:33,340 --> 00:12:34,820
♪When petals drift down♪

198
00:12:34,820 --> 00:12:36,320
♪When the rain falls all around♪

199
00:12:36,420 --> 00:12:38,980
♪I gaze into your eyes♪
